                     <hi rend="smallCaps">GUILTY</hi>
                  </rs>. <hi rend="italic">They were further charged with having been before convicted at Westminster, Donovan in October, 1866, and Lowry in June, 1856, to which they</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">PLEADED GUILTY</hi>. <hi rend="largeCaps">DONOVAN</hi>—<rs id="t18670610-581-punishment-51" type="punishmentDescription">
